# Break Away Puzzles

Up to now you only brought balls to the exit. 
This time things are different.

You may see the term "Break Away" in the upper right corner of your game screen.
That means that in order to solve this puzzle you must break away all the blocks in this puzzle.
The blocks will break as soon as a ball touches them.

As there is no exit please note that the $H statistic is not displayed. 
The number set by $C just displays how many balls must remain when the last block is removed.